data.description: Beautiful Cape Cod nestled on favorite cul-de-sac street in a prime location of Rocky River! Do not miss out on the deep 1/3 - acre lot, wow! Immaculate home offering updates throughout. Elegant details such as original hardwood floors, millwork and two fireplaces on the main floor. Spacious living room and dining room that opens to the kitchen for entertaining. Amazing great room addition (2020) offers tons of space for gathering, featuring a vaulted ceiling and sliders to the deck. Newly added mudroom (2020) off of the kitchen boasts a large pantry and easy access to driveway. Main level offers two large bedrooms and a full bath. Second level features a stunning oversized primary bedroom with an updated in-suite full bath, large closet, walk-in storage, large finished bonus area offering options for home office and more!  Additional living space is found in the lower recreation room, perfect for playtime & exercise! Neat & tidy laundry/utility room offers more storage. Enjoy all of the gorgeous outdoor space this home offers – meticulous landscape, composite deck & brick patio (2021) new custom designed fenced in raised garden, a convenient shed (2021) and the glorious deep, green backyard. Additional improvements include: Newer whole house windows, vinyl exterior sided home (2020), new garage doors (2021) & vinyl siding (2017), updated electric panel (2013). Truly a gem of a home! Exceptional location near Lake Erie, walk/bike to Elmwood Park, minutes to Whole Foods, Mitchell’s ice cream, Starbucks and Old River shopping & dining. Top rated schools. Immediate access to downtown CLE and Hopkins Airport.
